---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---
<Base
  title="About"
  description="Cartagena Up is a locally verified guide to Cartagena, Colombia — maintained by someone who lives here."
  lang="en"
  canonicalUrl="https://cartagenaup.com/about/">

  <div style="padding-top: 2rem;">
    <h1 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.875rem; color: var(--fg); margin: 0 0 1.75rem; line-height: 1.2;">
      About Cartagena Up
    </h1>

    <div style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.75; display: grid; gap: 1.25rem;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        Cartagena Up is maintained by two locals:
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Yatan</strong> has lived in Cartagena since 2021 and works remotely from the city. He tests WiFi speeds, tracks the cultural calendar, and runs <a href="https://casagaviota.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #C45C26; text-decoration: none;">Casa Gaviota</a>, a private beach house in Barú.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Adri</strong> has lived in Cartagena since 2010 — longer than almost any guide writer covering this city. She verifies cafés, knows the neighborhoods, and brings fifteen years of local knowledge to every listing.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        Every listing on this site was visited in person. Every WiFi speed is a real measurement. Every event comes from a local source.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        The events section tracks LGTBIQ+ events in Cartagena as a dedicated category — use the filter on the <a href="/events/" style="color: #C45C26; text-decoration: none;">events page</a> to find them. Cartagena has an active scene and it's underrepresented in most city guides.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        Something wrong or out of date? <a href="https://wa.me/573163946401?text=Hi! I want to send feedback about Cartagena Up." target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #C45C26; text-decoration: none;">Tell us on WhatsApp.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</Base>
